-------------------
How To Use PX fonts
-------------------

dvips:
        Add a line "p +pxr.map" into ${PREFIX}/${TEXMF}/dvips/base/config.ps.

dvipdfm:
        Add a line "f pxr3.map" into ${PREFIX}/${TEXMF}/dvipdfm/config/config.

(NOTE: This instruction depends on the directory layout of teTeX distribution.)
